  "elements": [
    {
      "id": "f6-guQlJyZQLlc9QU_A4C",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 319,
      "y": 145,
      "width": 1091.49560546875,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 897636130,
      "version": 234,
      "versionNonce": 735894818,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777094927026,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Proxy Design Pattern :- We need to make proxy object of an actual object, \nfor multiple reasons, proxy is exectly behaves like actual object and client cant \ndiffrentiate it.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Proxy Design Pattern :- We need to make proxy object of an actual object, \nfor multiple reasons, proxy is exectly behaves like actual object and client cant \ndiffrentiate it.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Q47M_mqpBiXwE19o6p7Vp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 364,
      "y": 312,
      "width": 1188.2392578125,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2050977854,
      "version": 349,
      "versionNonce": 1760596094,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777095013802,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Proxy can be with diffrent reasons like \n- Virtual proxy - Heavy operation of obejct creation, we dont want object to be created untill objecrt ka method is called\n- Protection proxy - Protecting actual object and adding validation checks\n- Remote Proxy ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Proxy can be with diffrent reasons like \n- Virtual proxy - Heavy operation of obejct creation, we dont want object to be created untill objecrt ka method is called\n- Protection proxy - Protecting actual object and adding validation checks\n- Remote Proxy ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "47M-tBjJFcVA2W8AgV4f-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 465,
      "width": 1066.6993408203125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 343751678,
      "version": 168,
      "versionNonce": 1323867774,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777095107931,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Proxy is representative of an actual resource, such that client does not know that if it is talking to actual \nobjject or proxy ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Proxy is representative of an actual resource, such that client does not know that if it is talking to actual \nobjject or proxy ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c_3tTn0SDS0y7Q7k1zsx_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 298.20001220703125,
      "y": 545.199951171875,
      "width": 1121.3198852539062,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 566626110,
      "version": 747,
      "versionNonce": 1435497506,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777095428976,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Virtual Proxy :- An actual object creation in construcutor or any way object creation is very very expensive and\ntime consuming process, also takes very much memory in RAM, hence if the object is created and it first takes\nmore time also takes so much memeory in RAM and it is wasted or just keeping the memory space untill its\nmethods is called that is called very less often, hence we want that the object should not be created untill its\nmehtod is called - That is actually use of the vitual proxy simple!!!",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Virtual Proxy :- An actual object creation in construcutor or any way object creation is very very expensive and time consuming process, also takes very much memory in RAM, hence if the object is created and it first takes more time also takes so much memeory in RAM and it is wasted or just keeping the memory space untill its methods is called that is called very less often, hence we want that the object should not be created untill its mehtod is called - That is actually use of the vitual proxy simple!!!",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
